title: What is the recipe for success on GBBO?
text:
What ingredients make a star baker? Do those pesky technical challenges really matter? Everything you (n)ever wanted to know about Love Productionâ€™s The Great British Bake Off is answered in graphs, using data from the bakeoff package in R.
As it turns out, people who scored higher in technicals made it farther overall!






Note: Series 1 had 6 episodes and Series 2 had 8, compared to the 10 from that point on
